com.sun.tools.javac.v8.util
类 List

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.tools.javac.v8.util.List

public final class List
extends java.lang.Object

A class for generic linked lists. Links are supposed to be immutable, the only exception being the incremental construction of lists via ListBuffers. List is the main container class in GJC. Most data structures and algorthms in GJC use lists rather than arrays. Lists are always trailed by a sentinel element, whose head and tail are both null.
